Class RfcBcelParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.obomprogramador.tools.jqana.model.AbstractMetricParser
      • com.obomprogramador.tools.jqana.parsers.RfcBcelParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parser

    public class RfcBcelParser
extends AbstractMetricParser
    This is a BCEL parser class, used to analyze RFC metric. To avoid compiler optimizations, I would have rather used only AST parsers (based on source code), but in the case of the metric RFC, the resulting parser would be very complex.
    Author:
    Cleuton Sampaio.
